[
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p000.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p001.jpg",
    "text": "Shit:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p002.jpg",
    "text": "What the hell do [ do against that?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p003.jpg",
    "text": "WORDINARY Episode 3"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p004.jpg",
    "text": "Haven't you learned?\nThe world doesn't have sympathy for weaklings like you:\nLay low and mind your own business__."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p005.jpg",
    "text": "Or keep getting in others' way and get killed:\nWas that threat?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p006.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p007.jpg",
    "text": "2 !"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p008.jpg",
    "text": "What?\nugh:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p009.jpg",
    "text": "He's so fast!"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p010.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p011.jpg",
    "text": "Just now, his skin was rock solid.\nIncreased speed and durability-?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p012.jpg",
    "text": "Oh, / get it?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p013.jpg",
    "text": "He has flashy power-up\nBut his ability is just form of self- enhancement?"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p014.jpg",
    "text": "That was only a taste of what can do.\nIf you beg me, VIl let you leave here in one piece:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p015.jpg",
    "text": "Seriously? Your ability isn't even that good.\nYou're just\ngloating because you finally found someone weaker than you:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p016.jpg",
    "text": "Snile ."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p017.jpg",
    "text": "Pft .\nMHM AHAL"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p018.jpg",
    "text": "What the hell are you laughing at?\nYou; of coursel"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p019.jpg",
    "text": "Beg? That's a pretty big demand:\nUsually, when someone talks like that, he can back it up."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p020.jpg",
    "text": "Let me give you some examples .\nGupk"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p021.jpg",
    "text": "So, we have Remi who could burn me to a crisp.\nBlyke and Isen who are currently blowing up Wallik Hall:\nshaflle \"\n2"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p022.jpg",
    "text": ":And obviously, Seraphina, who is pretty much a god."
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p023.jpg",
    "text": "Okay, your turn?\nWhat can you do?\nMove a little faster?\nHit a little harder?\n%"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p024.jpg",
    "text": "Doesn't seem too threatening"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p025.jpg",
    "text": "In fact_\nbet [\ncould beat you even without an ability:\nSmp:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p026.jpg",
    "text": "You:._\nSHUT THE F*CK UPW"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p027.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p028.jpg",
    "text": "Huh?!\nGPab"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p029.jpg",
    "text": "Hhl"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p030.jpg",
    "text": "9"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p031.jpg",
    "text": ""
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p032.jpg",
    "text": "HOLY SHIT'\nThat actually worked? pissed Almost  wysalf"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p033.jpg",
    "text": "My arm though:.\nIt's broken again:"
  },
  {
    "path": "data\\raw\\panels\\unordinary\\ep_4\\unordinary_ep4_p034.jpg",
    "text": "Oh man:._"
